Package vidis.data.var.vars

Class Summary
DefaultVariable a default variable implementation
FieldVariable a field variable; this class uses reflection to get the contents of a field variable in a certain object.
MethodVariable a method variable; this variable uses reflection to retrieve the value, just like its little brother FieldVariable does.
